    "en": {
      "title": "A person is suspected with 20 lakhs of ganja",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A suspect was arrested by the Special Task Force in Kirulapana along with a stock of Kerala Ganja worth over twenty lakh rupees.",
        "According to information that the suspect is ready to sell a stock of Kerala ganja, the troops have conducted this raid.",
        "At the time of arrest, the suspect was in possession of more than 6 kilos of Kerala Ganja Kerala Ganja.",
        "The arrested suspect is a resident of Kirulapana area and he and the stock of Kerala ganja have been handed over to the Kirulapana police for further investigations."
      ],
